#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Task Editor is a view that displays task data in a tree structure. Most "
"data in the Task Editor can be edited in situ."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik nalog je pogled, ki prikazuje podatke naloge v drevesni "
"strukturi. Večino podatkov v urejevalniku nalog je mogoče urejati na mestu."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "Krmarjenje"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can navigate the tree structure using the keyboard:"
msgstr "Po drevesni strukturi lahko krmarite s tipkovnico:"

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>+</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>+</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand an expandable row."
msgstr "Razširi razširljivo vrstico."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>-</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>-</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collapse a collapsible item."
msgstr "Strni zložljiv element."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow left"
msgstr "Puščica levo"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to previous column in the same row."
msgstr "Pojdi na prejšnji stolpec v isti vrstici."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow right"
msgstr "Puščica desno"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to next column in the same row."
msgstr "Pojdi na naslednji stolpec v isti vrstici."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow up"
msgstr "Puščica navzgor"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to previous row in the same column."
msgstr "Pojdi na prejšnjo vrstico v istem stolpcu."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow down"
msgstr "Puščica navzdol"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to next row in the same column."
msgstr "Pojdi na naslednjo vrstico v istem stolpcu."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Domov"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to first row, first column."
msgstr "Pojdi na prvo vrstico, prvi stolpec."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>End</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>Konec</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to last row, last column."
msgstr "Pojdi na zadnjo vrstico, zadnji stolpec."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page up"
msgstr "Stran gor"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to first visible row in the same column."
msgstr "Pojdi na prvo vidno vrstico v istem stolpcu."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page down"
msgstr "Stran navzdol"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to last visible row in the same column."
msgstr "Pojdi na zadnjo vidno vrstico v istem stolpcu."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Urejanje podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Editable items are opened for editing by double-clicking on the item or, if "
"using the keyboard, pressing <keycap>F2</keycap> will open the current item."
msgstr ""
"Elemente, ki jih je mogoče urejati, odprete za urejanje z dvojnim klikom na "
"element ali, če uporabljate tipkovnico, s pritiskom <keycap>F2</keycap> "
"odprete trenutni element."

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When editing an item you can navigate to the next editable item as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Ko urejate element, se lahko pomaknete do naslednjega elementa, ki ga je "
"mogoče urejati, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow left</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Puščica levo</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous editable item in the same row."
msgstr "Pojdi na prejšnji element, ki ga je mogoče urejati, v isti vrstici."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow right</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Puščica desno</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in the same row."
msgstr "Pojdi na naslednji element, ki ga je mogoče urejati, v isti vrstici."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow up</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Puščica navzgor</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in preceding rows."
msgstr ""
"Pojdi na naslednji element, ki ga je mogoče urejati, v prejšnjih vrsticah."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow down</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Puščica navzdol</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in succeeding rows."
msgstr ""
"Pojdi na naslednji element, ki ga je mogoče urejati, v naslednjih vrsticah."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag &amp; drop and copy/paste"
msgstr "Povleci &amp; spusti in kopiraj/prilepi"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most views support drag &amp; drop and copy/paste. Charts and Gantt charts "
"can be dragged to applications that support images. Table data uses the html "
"mime type, so can be dropped on any applications that supports this. If the "
"view supports moving or copying items internally &eg; the <link linkend="
"\"task-editor\">Task Editor</link>, items can also be moved or copied."
msgstr ""
"Večina pogledov podpira povleci &amp; spusti in kopiraj/prilepi. Grafe in "
"Ganttove diagrame lahko povlečete v aplikacije, ki podpirajo slike. Podatki "
"tabele uporabljajo vrsto html mime, zato jih je mogoče izpustiti v kateri "
"koli aplikaciji, ki to podpira. Če pogled podpira notranje premikanje ali "
"kopiranje elementov &eg; <link linkend=\"task-editor\">Urejevalnik nalog</"
"link>, lahko elemente tudi premaknete ali kopirate."
